ABOUT THIS GAME:

Spider Wizard is an exciting solitaire card game based on the
classic game Spider. Spider Wizard contains not only Spider, but
15 other similar games, including Spider One Suit and Spider Two
Suits, Miss Milligan, Scorpion, Spiderette, Rouge et Noir, and
Simple Simon. You can create your own Spider variations using
the Spider Wizard. You can undo all your moves, automatically
save a game in progress, and make moves with a single mouse
click.
